Rating: 3
The way I made this, I would rate it 3 1/2 forks. I minced up one clove of garlic and sauteed that in the butter first. Next, I added about 1 1/2 cups of leftover cooked chicken with the sage and breadcrumbs. It was a great and delicious way to use up leftovers. Also, I used vermicelli instead of elbow macaroni. This was a wonderful quick meal.

